    "summary": "The user asks about the economic impacts of federal environmental regulations on small manufacturers, specifically probing whether these rules favor large corporations and ignore small business survival. The assistant provides a balanced view, acknowledging the financial hurdles for small shops while explaining the regulatory focus on environmental benchmarks.",
